1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:25,789 --> 00:01:30,030
[My Heart]

3
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,800
[Episode 13]

4
00:01:53,140 --> 00:01:53,700
My lady,

5
00:01:56,970 --> 00:01:57,940
Why are you here?

6
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:00,380
Nangong!

7
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,300
Why are you getting worse?

8
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:07,140
Should I call Master Rongyun here?

9
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:08,020
Don't bother.

10
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:11,340
You're holding a letter.

11
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:13,700
Did anything happen?

12
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:14,500
Yeah.

13
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:15,500
Xiaowu sent a letter,

14
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:17,460
said that the Empress sent troops to lay siege to Lu Mansion

15
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:19,450
because Lu Qingqing deceived royalty

16
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:21,060
and cheated Her Majesty with the fake treasure.

17
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:28,690
The fake treasure?

18
00:02:29,329 --> 00:02:30,540
How could there be the fake treasure?

19
00:02:31,210 --> 00:02:32,540
The fusang fruit that you picked

20
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:34,060
turned to be a stone!

21
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:35,180
Impossible!

22
00:02:35,620 --> 00:02:36,740
It can't be fake!

23
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:40,250
I remember, before I gave it to you,

24
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:42,100
I had checked it over.

25
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:44,300
I don't know about the rest.

26
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:47,500
Then is my father all right now?

27
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:50,740
Lord Lu is confined in his study room and is not allowed to go out.

28
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:52,579
Today he fell ill

29
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,700
due to anxiety and weakness.

30
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:56,500
My fatehr is sick?

31
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:59,300
No... No way...

32
00:03:00,210 --> 00:03:01,660
I was there when she picked the fusang fruit.

33
00:03:02,530 --> 00:03:03,740
It can't be fake!

34
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:06,820
Besides...

35
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:09,180
Besides, the treasures have been handed over for so long.

36
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:11,100
They didn't mention it until now.

37
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:12,540
It's so strange.

38
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:14,020
Then do you have any idea?

39
00:03:14,460 --> 00:03:16,260
Lu Qingqing was assassinated by a man in black several days before.

40
00:03:17,540 --> 00:03:18,940
And next, these things happened to Lu Mansion today.

41
00:03:20,380 --> 00:03:21,140
It's more than a coincidence!

42
00:03:22,020 --> 00:03:25,380
Someone must have schemed it on purpose.

43
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:27,180
I also think it's not a simple case.

44
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:28,980
Even if the treasure is fake,

45
00:03:29,780 --> 00:03:30,579
Her Majesty shouldn't have

46
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:31,860
punished all the people in Lu Mansion.

47
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:33,740
And it hasn't been three months yet.

48
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:36,020
They're so anxious and reckless now.

49
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:38,420
Is it because of...

50
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:46,220
The magic power stone.

51
00:03:46,820 --> 00:03:47,380
Make way!

52
00:03:48,380 --> 00:03:48,900
Mother,

53
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:51,050
why are you punishing Qingqing and people in Lu Mansion?

54
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:52,420
Didn't she bring back the three treasures

55
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:53,660
as you commanded?

56
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:56,500
Lu Qingqing deceived me with a fake treasure.

57
00:03:57,060 --> 00:04:00,060
She definitely has no respect for me.

58
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:03,020
Seems like she doesn't want to come back to Qiyuan.

59
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:04,060
The treasure is fake?

60
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:07,540
Mr. Lu and I saw it in person.

61
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:09,970
You can go ask him if you don't believe it.

62
00:04:12,339 --> 00:04:14,339
I think it's not the whole story.

63
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:15,899
Qingqing wouldn't do it deliberately!

64
00:04:16,220 --> 00:04:16,820
Mingyang,

65
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:20,180
I do it all for you!

66
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:22,300
If you do it for me,

67
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,340
please stop giving Qingqing a hard time, okay?

68
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:25,620
I have my own reason.

69
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:26,900
Stop it now.

70
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:27,740
Mother!

71
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:28,340
Enough!

72
00:04:28,980 --> 00:04:29,820
I'm tired.

73
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:30,980
Mudan,

74
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:32,220
send His Highness out.

75
00:04:33,930 --> 00:04:34,659
Your Highness.

76
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:51,659
Stand up.

77
00:04:54,620 --> 00:04:56,580
Why did you greet me so formally today?

78
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:59,740
Something urgent happened to my family.

79
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:01,220
I have to go back immediately.

80
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:03,060
So I'm here to bid farewell to you, Master.

81
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:04,020
What happened?

82
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:06,380
Something's wrong with the fusang fruit,

83
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,620
one of the three treasures I asked others

84
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:08,900
to send to the Empress.

85
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:10,660
Her Majesty was furious,

86
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,660
and sent people to confine my family.

87
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,890
I'm accountable for it.

88
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:16,700
So I need to go back to address it.

89
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:19,700
I see.

90
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:21,940
If so,

91
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:23,620
I won't put you on the spot.

92
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,380
But should you

93
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:26,740
go negotiate it with you senior, too?

94
00:05:29,610 --> 00:05:30,450
No need to do so.

95
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,330
He's not willing to see me.

96
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:38,820
Now that you'll go back,

97
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:40,530
it's unnecessary to wear this distance bracelet.

98
00:05:41,140 --> 00:05:42,620
As for whether you'll see your senior or not,

99
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,260
it depends on you.

100
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:43,100
Well,

101
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:45,420
don't get me wrong.

102
00:06:46,090 --> 00:06:47,380
I'm not here for you.

103
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:49,060
I'm just passing by.

104
00:06:50,659 --> 00:06:51,780
I didn't allow you to go inside,

105
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:54,690
so you just guarded outside the door.

106
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,900
And now I finally came out,

107
00:06:59,180 --> 00:06:59,900
but you'll run away.

108
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:02,050
I...

109
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:07,340
Where's your distance bracelet?

110
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:12,900
Master has removed it.

111
00:07:14,700 --> 00:07:15,740
I'm going back to my home,

112
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:18,860
so naturally, this bracelet is useless.

113
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:21,020
Did you say you're going back to home?

114
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:22,420
No way!

115
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:24,020
You can't go back!

116
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:25,780
What happened to Lu Mansion is so suspicious.

117
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,659
So you knew it!

118
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,500
Suspicious?

119
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:33,780
Why?

120
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,300
They just want the magic...

121
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:40,700
I-I mean,

122
00:07:41,659 --> 00:07:42,500
did it ever occur to you

123
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,380
that there's some connections

124
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:45,620
between you being assassinated

125
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:47,380
and Lu Mansion's being besieged?

126
00:07:47,650 --> 00:07:48,580
You'd better be cautious.

127
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,180
No matter what,

128
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:53,860
this is caused by me.

129
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:56,740
I can't let my family take the punishment for me.

130
00:07:57,860 --> 00:08:00,300
I should take the consequences for what I did.

131
00:08:01,260 --> 00:08:02,700
Didn't you say it to me

132
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:05,090
when we were in No Magic Valley?

133
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,660
I should care about not only my own feelings,

134
00:08:08,140 --> 00:08:09,140
but also others'.

135
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:12,540
Then I'll go back with you.

136
00:08:17,180 --> 00:08:17,660
Don't bother.

137
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:20,300
My magic level is five now.

138
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:22,060
I can take good care of myself.

139
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,580
You just rest well to recover.

140
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:28,580
Then I can rest assured.

141
00:08:58,540 --> 00:08:58,980
Oh, no!

142
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,020
Stay here and wait for me.

143
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:31,860
Lin Sheng!

144
00:09:33,540 --> 00:09:34,060
Lin Sheng!

145
00:09:34,660 --> 00:09:35,140
Lin Sheng!

146
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:36,220
What happened?

147
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:38,340
Wan Qing,

148
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:40,580
If I leave this world,

149
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,780
remember to take care of yourself.

150
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:44,780
No...

151
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:48,660
No!

152
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,620
No, Lin Sheng! No!

153
00:09:51,140 --> 00:09:53,500
Lin Sheng... Lin Sheng...

154
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:55,140
Wake up!

155
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:14,600
[There's an Emergency. Come Back Soon. Wan Qing.]

156
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:23,820
Master.

157
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,580
You know me the best.

158
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:36,620
You knew I would come.

159
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:37,980
Take your time.

160
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:40,060
Have some tea first.

161
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:42,420
I have something urgent to do.

162
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:43,900
Thank you

163
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:45,940
for taking care of me these days.

164
00:10:46,300 --> 00:10:47,340
How do you feel now?

165
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:48,420
I'm okay.

166
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:57,860
I've persuaded you so many times

167
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,780
to keep calm no matter what happens.

168
00:11:00,500 --> 00:11:02,060
Once you panic, it's easy to make mistakes.

169
00:11:02,460 --> 00:11:04,860
Once you take a false step, things will foul up.

170
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:06,860
You can't do it

171
00:11:07,890 --> 00:11:09,100
when it's not the right time yet.

172
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,090
Master,

173
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,740
I don't ask for anything else.

174
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:17,820
I just hope she could be safe.

175
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:20,220
Then even if it does harm to you when you're with her,

176
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:21,540
will you still do it?

177
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:23,650
She's the one who I must protect whatever it takes.

178
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:26,500
As for the consequences,

179
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:29,220
I'll calmly accepet them.

180
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:36,740
Thank you for supporting me, Master.

181
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:42,540
[Great Virtue]

182
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:54,930
[Lu Mansion]

183
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:52,420
Stop there!

184
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:53,780
Lu Mansion is the forbidden area now.

185
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:54,940
No one is allowed to enter.

186
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:56,260
This is my home.

187
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:57,690
I'm the second lady of Lu Family.

188
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:58,420
Get out of my way!

189
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,180
Lu Qingqing!

190
00:11:59,420 --> 00:11:59,940
Arrest her!

191
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,300
Magic Level Five?

192
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:19,780
You don't need to arrest me.

193
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:21,420
When the truth comes to light,

194
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:22,740
you can do whatever you want.

195
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:27,190
[Lu Mansion]

196
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:38,620
What happened to Lu Mansion?

197
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:39,220
My lady,

198
00:12:39,540 --> 00:12:41,220
the fusang fruit you asked Commander Qi to take back

199
00:12:41,380 --> 00:12:43,580
was discovered to be fake when it was handed over to Her Majesty.

200
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:46,380
Her Majesty said you deceived royalty,

201
00:12:46,780 --> 00:12:47,420
and was impenitent.

202
00:12:48,060 --> 00:12:49,220
So Her Majesty sent troops to besiege Lu Mansion,

203
00:12:49,860 --> 00:12:50,740
and said you were wanted.

204
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:53,570
Her Majesty also said Lord Lu didn't educate you properly.

205
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:55,380
So Lord Lu got punished with 100 magic whips!

206
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:57,940
These days,

207
00:12:58,580 --> 00:12:59,820
many of the staff in the mansion

208
00:13:00,060 --> 00:13:00,660
have left.

209
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:02,860
Right, and Baihe!

210
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:04,020
What happened to Baihe?

211
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:05,860
Baihe has been locked at the woodshed.

212
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:07,780
Lord Lu could send people to take care of her before.

213
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,300
But now everything in our mansion

214
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,580
is intervened by Her Majesty's people.

215
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:13,060
Baihe hasn't eaten for several days!

216
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:14,220
I'm afraid...

217
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:22,940
Baihe!

218
00:13:23,410 --> 00:13:24,220
Are you there?

219
00:13:24,660 --> 00:13:25,620
Can you here me?

220
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,180
My lady!

221
00:13:27,660 --> 00:13:28,540
Why did you come back?

222
00:13:28,820 --> 00:13:30,460
Go! Leave here now!

223
00:13:30,970 --> 00:13:31,980
They're trying to catch you!

224
00:13:40,850 --> 00:13:41,260
Baihe!

225
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:45,690
It's all my fault.

226
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:49,250
My lady,

227
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:50,500
I'm okay.

228
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:52,460
It's good to see you safe and sound.

229
00:13:54,580 --> 00:13:55,820
You are implicated because of me.

230
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:58,260
I thought if I gave the three treasures to Her Majesty,

231
00:13:58,700 --> 00:13:59,700
they would exonerate you.

232
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:01,260
But I didn't expect...

233
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:05,300
I should have come back earlier.

234
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:07,260
It's just an accident.

235
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:08,820
I don't blame you.

236
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,500
Let's go. I'll help you out first.

237
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:25,100
Wan Qing!

238
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:27,860
How's it going with Xiaoyi?

239
00:14:28,130 --> 00:14:29,620
I've got medicine for him from Doctor Wu.

240
00:14:30,060 --> 00:14:31,100
He ate and fell asleep.

241
00:14:32,420 --> 00:14:33,300
What on earth happened?

242
00:14:35,860 --> 00:14:36,660
Let's go there to talk.

243
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:41,340
The magic power army acted so rampantly in No Magic Valley.

244
00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:43,460
So hateful!

245
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:46,220
Xiaoyi's parents were murdered right by this army.

246
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:48,660
Seeing this occasion today,

247
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:49,460
he definitely couldn't stand it.

248
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:51,260
Today I called you to come over.

249
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:52,940
For one thing, it's for Xiaoyi.

250
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,060
For another thing,

251
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:56,340
I want to join the Red Face Army.

252
00:14:57,820 --> 00:14:58,340
What?

253
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,340
I said I want to join the Red Face Army,

254
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:01,940
to fight against the magic power army

255
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:04,380
and take revenge.

256
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:05,460
Wan Qing!

257
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,740
What on earth happened between you and the magic power army?

258
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:13,340
If you're reluctant to tell it,

259
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:14,900
I won't force you.

260
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:16,780
But I suggest you think twice.

261
00:15:18,660 --> 00:15:19,900
I don't approve of your joining the Red Face Army.

262
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:21,900
Why?

263
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:24,900
Do you think I'm weak?

264
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:27,660
I can do everything that you can do!

265
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:28,940
It's not because of this.

266
00:15:29,660 --> 00:15:30,500
Then why?

267
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:32,620
Do you think I'll be scared?

268
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:34,140
I know,

269
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:36,180
the duty of the Red Face Army is to protect our people.

270
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:38,340
For their safety,

271
00:15:38,620 --> 00:15:40,300
the army will risk their own lives.

272
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:41,140
I can do it, too!

273
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:42,060
I can do everything!

274
00:15:42,220 --> 00:15:42,820
Wan Qing!

275
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:45,340
To join the Red Face Army, it relies not on passion,

276
00:15:46,290 --> 00:15:47,380
but composure and ability.

277
00:15:48,220 --> 00:15:49,060
And the Red Face Army exists

278
00:15:49,060 --> 00:15:50,060
not only for sacrifice,

279
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:53,460
It's for our people and ourselves to live better!

280
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:04,740
Wan Qing,

281
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,660
the magic power army acted so rampantly in No Magic Valley.

282
00:16:07,660 --> 00:16:08,660
As the Commander's son,

283
00:16:08,660 --> 00:16:10,180
I'll surely do something for it.

284
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:12,620
Trust me.

285
00:16:19,180 --> 00:16:19,740
What's more,

286
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,660
children at Ciyou Kindergarten can't live without you.

287
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:23,780
Take care of them.

288
00:16:24,860 --> 00:16:26,020
And I'll go deal with the magic power army.

289
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:52,180
Be careful.

290
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:53,730
Qingqing!

291
00:16:54,140 --> 00:16:55,060
You're finally home!

292
00:16:55,860 --> 00:16:56,300
Father,

293
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,180
are you all right?

294
00:16:59,099 --> 00:17:00,180
Father fell ill right after he came back.

295
00:17:00,900 --> 00:17:01,660
At such an old age,

296
00:17:01,980 --> 00:17:03,300
he still took all the 100 magic whips.

297
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:04,540
Hearing your coming back,

298
00:17:04,740 --> 00:17:05,980
Father came out to see you right away.

299
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:07,660
Without any investigation

300
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,050
or hard evidence,

301
00:17:09,290 --> 00:17:10,579
how could they whip Father?

302
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:12,300
Sorry, I didn't know that

303
00:17:13,339 --> 00:17:14,900
during the time I stayed in Manghuang forest,

304
00:17:15,300 --> 00:17:16,619
Lu Mansion suffered such a catastrophe.

305
00:17:17,740 --> 00:17:18,730
It's okay.

306
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:19,740
Qingqing,

307
00:17:20,410 --> 00:17:21,740
you shouldn't have come back.

308
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:25,460
No matter what happens, I can carry it for you.

309
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:27,140
Qingqing...

310
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:31,180
Father,

311
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:32,340
I'm sorry.

312
00:17:32,980 --> 00:17:34,140
This case was caused by me.

313
00:17:34,580 --> 00:17:36,100
I'll surely find a way to solve it.

314
00:17:37,620 --> 00:17:39,700
My Qingqing has grown up.

315
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:41,780
Qi Yi!

316
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:43,660
What on earth happened to the fusang fruit?

317
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:45,460
I took the three treasures

318
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:46,980
to Lord Lu intact.

319
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:48,940
As for the fake fusang fruit, however,

320
00:17:49,140 --> 00:17:50,380
I really have no idea.

321
00:17:51,090 --> 00:17:53,220
I picked it from the tree by myself.

322
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:54,660
How can it be fake?

323
00:17:55,060 --> 00:17:56,420
I also find it weird.

324
00:17:57,860 --> 00:17:58,580
Lord Lu!

325
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:05,500
Who is Lu Qingqing?

326
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:09,700
It's me. What do you want?

327
00:18:10,010 --> 00:18:11,380
According to Her Majesty's edict,

328
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,660
we're here to arrest the second lady of Lu Family.

329
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:14,940
Please go with me.

330
00:18:14,940 --> 00:18:16,300
When the truth comes to light,

331
00:18:16,580 --> 00:18:17,540
I will go with you.

332
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:18,860
But not now.

333
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:21,340
It's not up to you.

334
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:22,460
How dare you.

335
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:23,940
This is Lu Mansion.

336
00:18:24,060 --> 00:18:24,700
I won't let you

337
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:26,610
take my daughter away so easily.

338
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:27,780
Great Commander,

339
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:29,660
can you let us get to the bottom of it first,

340
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:30,620
and then go to apologize to Her Majesty?

341
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:33,140
My daughter is always upright.

342
00:18:33,330 --> 00:18:34,580
This is definitely not the whole story!

343
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:36,860
Hope you can go back to report to Her Majesty,

344
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:38,780
and make a decision after we find out the truth.

345
00:18:39,180 --> 00:18:39,850
Lord Lu,

346
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:42,020
you're harboring a felon!

347
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:43,660
If you keep stopping us,

348
00:18:44,020 --> 00:18:45,540
I'll show no mercy.

349
00:18:50,660 --> 00:18:51,140
Stop.

350
00:18:52,020 --> 00:18:53,060
This happened because of me.

351
00:18:53,490 --> 00:18:54,660
I won't get my family into trouble.

352
00:18:56,850 --> 00:18:57,460
Great Commander.

353
00:19:04,060 --> 00:19:04,780
Your Highness.

354
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:08,410
Why are you using force here?

355
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:09,980
According to Her Majesty's edict,

356
00:19:10,220 --> 00:19:13,060
I must capture Lu Qingqing today.

357
00:19:13,780 --> 00:19:15,540
Lu Qingqing just returned from Manghuang forest.

358
00:19:15,860 --> 00:19:16,740
She's exhausted.

359
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:18,060
And it's not the right time to investigate.

360
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:20,300
Make other arrangements after she takes a rest.

361
00:19:20,810 --> 00:19:21,380
Well...

362
00:19:25,220 --> 00:19:27,220
I'll go explain to my mother.

363
00:19:31,220 --> 00:19:31,620
What?

364
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:34,460
Are my words useless now?

365
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,500
As you command, Your Highness.

366
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:44,180
You can leave, too.

367
00:19:45,540 --> 00:19:46,820
Thank you, Your Highness.

368
00:19:47,980 --> 00:19:48,940
Don't mention it, Mr. Lu.

369
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:49,860
I can't just wait and see

370
00:19:50,180 --> 00:19:51,260
when it comes to Qingqing.

371
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:52,660
Your Highness,

372
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,340
will Her Majesty blame you?

373
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:57,780
There must be some misunderstandings.

374
00:19:58,340 --> 00:19:59,140
I trust Qingqing.

375
00:20:00,340 --> 00:20:01,020
I will go explain to Mother.

376
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:03,540
Thank you for your help, Your Highness.

377
00:20:03,980 --> 00:20:04,500
So long as you're safe,

378
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:06,100
I can rest assured.

379
00:20:07,020 --> 00:20:08,060
But I can't.

380
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:10,180
You've helped me out for several times these days.

381
00:20:10,940 --> 00:20:13,130
I just feel I owe you so much.

382
00:20:13,620 --> 00:20:14,220
You and I don't need

383
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:16,020
to be so polite to each other.

384
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:20,660
This matter was caused by me.

385
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:22,260
I can't run away from it.

386
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:24,420
I'll go with you to meet Her Majesty in the palace,

387
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:25,700
and explain it to her.

388
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:27,500
I'll be by your side.

389
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:32,400
[Lu Mansion]

390
00:20:31,860 --> 00:20:32,740
Please wait, Your Highness.

391
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:33,140
Stop there!

392
00:20:33,660 --> 00:20:34,380
As Her Majesty orders,

393
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:36,100
no one in Lu Mansion can get out.

394
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,020
Then why can Lu Qingqing go outside?

395
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,380
She's the chief culprit!

396
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:41,820
Lady Qingqing is going

397
00:20:41,820 --> 00:20:42,540
with His Highness!

398
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:43,500
Let her come.

399
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:45,380
Yes, Your Highness.

400
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:48,180
Thank you, Your Highness.

401
00:20:51,660 --> 00:20:52,180
Qingqing,

402
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:54,940
remember to be cautious when you talk and act in the palace.

403
00:20:55,460 --> 00:20:56,820
Don't offend Her Majesty.

404
00:20:57,540 --> 00:20:58,780
As for the fake fusang fruit,

405
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:00,940
you made a mistake first, anyway.

406
00:21:01,450 --> 00:21:01,980
Yunxi,

407
00:21:02,260 --> 00:21:04,810
the one I picked is the genuine fusang fruit.

408
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:06,260
Believe me.

409
00:21:06,930 --> 00:21:08,740
I will admit mistakes I make.

410
00:21:09,100 --> 00:21:09,980
But I will never admit

411
00:21:10,100 --> 00:21:11,060
to what I didn't do.

412
00:21:11,460 --> 00:21:12,940
Lady Qingqing, you'd better not act recklessly

413
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,100
and ruin the entire Lu Mansion.

414
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:15,060
Zhenzhu!

415
00:21:16,860 --> 00:21:18,180
Of course I believe you.

416
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:20,370
But before we get to the bottom of it,

417
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:22,500
remember to keep calm.

418
00:21:23,260 --> 00:21:24,380
This is also for Father.

419
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:27,300
He's greatly influenced by this matter.

420
00:21:27,730 --> 00:21:29,410
Don't let him worried about you again.

421
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:31,580
Then take good care of Father.

422
00:21:32,020 --> 00:21:33,500
I'm going to get a clear picture.

423
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:34,650
And I'll be back soon.

424
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,380
Qingqing,

425
00:21:37,140 --> 00:21:38,820
it's lucky for you to have such an elder sister.

426
00:21:39,690 --> 00:21:40,820
She's always caring about you

427
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,210
and worried about your safety.

428
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:43,860
Did you meet her

429
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:45,540
when she went to Manghuang forest

430
00:21:46,140 --> 00:21:46,780
regardless of the danger?

431
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:49,620
You've been to Manghuang forest, Yunxi?

432
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:51,890
Then why didn't I see you?

433
00:21:55,100 --> 00:21:56,290
I worried that you alone

434
00:21:56,290 --> 00:21:57,620
might run into danger in Manghuang forest,

435
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:59,220
so I went to visit you.

436
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:01,060
But I failed to find you.

437
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,540
Maybe,

438
00:22:02,810 --> 00:22:04,540
you were already in Youhuang at that time.

439
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:07,580
I see.

440
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:10,340
Then did you come up against the liger?

441
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:12,420
It's too dangerous in Manghuang forest.

442
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,700
You'd better not go there again.

443
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:14,460
No, I didn't.

444
00:22:15,060 --> 00:22:17,060
I didn't find you, and then I just came back.

445
00:22:18,540 --> 00:22:20,740
I didn't care about your feelings.

446
00:22:21,180 --> 00:22:22,060
It's my fault.

447
00:22:23,060 --> 00:22:23,610
Qingqing,

448
00:22:24,220 --> 00:22:26,420
you should handle things cautiously in the palace.

449
00:22:27,540 --> 00:22:28,020
Your Highness,

450
00:22:28,450 --> 00:22:29,490
I'll leave Qingqing to you.

451
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:32,300
Let's go, Qingqing.

452
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:38,190
[Lu Mansion]

453
00:22:41,040 --> 00:22:43,190
[Lord Jin Mansion]

454
00:22:50,700 --> 00:22:51,220
Your Highness,

455
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:52,380
you've finally back!

456
00:22:52,940 --> 00:22:54,260
Loads of things happened during this time.

457
00:22:54,740 --> 00:22:56,260
Now Lu Mansion is completely besieged,

458
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:57,820
and Lady Qingqing is even wanted!

459
00:22:58,420 --> 00:22:59,060
Nevertheless,

460
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:01,300
I heard that Lady Qingqing came back by herself.

461
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:02,660
I know she's back.

462
00:23:02,980 --> 00:23:04,940
And she's been taken to the palace by the Crown Prince.

463
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:05,580
To the palace?

464
00:23:07,580 --> 00:23:09,060
Then Her Majesty won't let her go!

465
00:23:09,620 --> 00:23:11,580
The Lu Family is involved in this matter

466
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:13,740
So nothing serious will happen for now.

467
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:14,980
But I insist

468
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:17,100
what happened to the fusang fruit is abnormal.

469
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,060
To find out the truth now,

470
00:23:19,260 --> 00:23:20,380
what matters most is

471
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,020
to find out where the real fusang fruit is.

472
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:23,490
Your Highness, you mean,

473
00:23:24,060 --> 00:23:25,900
what Lady Qingqing picked is the real fusang fruit,

474
00:23:26,620 --> 00:23:27,780
but it was changed by someone.

475
00:23:31,220 --> 00:23:31,740
Your Highness

476
00:23:32,060 --> 00:23:32,860
you had been with

477
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:34,300
Lady Qingqing all this time.

478
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:35,860
Will you be involved?

479
00:23:39,340 --> 00:23:40,220
Now,

480
00:23:40,730 --> 00:23:42,140
my condition is less important.

481
00:23:42,660 --> 00:23:43,700
Qingqing is of the first priority.

482
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:49,100
Many things have happened to Lady Qingqing recently.

483
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,060
Greetings, Mother.

484
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:54,700
Greetings, Your Majesty.

485
00:23:55,060 --> 00:23:55,780
Mingyang,

486
00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:57,420
this case has nothing to do with you.

487
00:23:57,660 --> 00:23:59,300
Why do you have to get involved?

488
00:24:00,100 --> 00:24:01,980
Unruly as Lu Qingqing is,

489
00:24:02,420 --> 00:24:04,660
she used the fake fusang fruit to deceive me.

490
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:07,180
Am I wrong to catch her?

491
00:24:07,660 --> 00:24:09,420
Did she pay any respect for

492
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:10,580
our Nangong royalty?

493
00:24:11,020 --> 00:24:11,820
-Mother! -Your Majesty.

494
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:13,020
I picked

495
00:24:13,180 --> 00:24:15,100
that fusang fruit in Manghuang forest myself.

496
00:24:15,580 --> 00:24:16,700
How can it be fake?

497
00:24:17,490 --> 00:24:18,780
If I did anything wrong,

498
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:20,850
please just bring it up directly.

499
00:24:20,900 --> 00:24:22,700
You don't need to frame me in this way.

500
00:24:23,340 --> 00:24:24,210
What a girl!

501
00:24:24,580 --> 00:24:26,420
How dare you say that I frame you?

502
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:27,500
Good.

503
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:29,340
Seems like you won't yield

504
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:30,620
until I show you the truth.

505
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:34,340
Open your eyes and look at it!

506
00:24:34,340 --> 00:24:36,140
Is it a stone or the fusang fruit?

507
00:24:41,180 --> 00:24:42,220
How could this be?

508
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:43,130
Great Commander!

509
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,780
Lock Lu Qingqing up!

510
00:24:44,860 --> 00:24:45,300
Yes, Your Majesty.

511
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:45,940
Great Commander!

512
00:24:46,690 --> 00:24:47,100
Mother,

513
00:24:47,380 --> 00:24:48,300
this is fake.

514
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:49,780
But could it be changed

515
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:50,900
when it was delivered?

516
00:24:51,330 --> 00:24:53,140
I hope you can give Qingqing some days

517
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:54,380
to find out the truth.

518
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,660
It's apparently her fault!

519
00:24:56,020 --> 00:24:57,140
You harbor her so willfully.

520
00:24:57,380 --> 00:24:58,220
Do you remember the rules?

521
00:24:59,300 --> 00:24:59,780
Mother!

522
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:01,410
Qingqing said she didn't do it.

523
00:25:01,660 --> 00:25:02,780
And I trust her.

524
00:25:02,860 --> 00:25:03,860
This is really not the whole story.

525
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:05,810
Please give her several days

526
00:25:06,100 --> 00:25:07,060
to get to the bottom of it.

527
00:25:07,220 --> 00:25:07,660
You!

528
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:28,200
[Jinghui Gate]

529
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:20,220
Your Highness.

530
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:22,260
thank you so much this time.

531
00:25:23,140 --> 00:25:24,420
You not only solved the problem for Lu Mansion,

532
00:25:24,860 --> 00:25:26,260
but also bought me time.

533
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:28,420
I don't even know how to pay you back.

534
00:25:28,420 --> 00:25:29,020
Qingqing,

535
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:30,780
don't mention it.

536
00:25:31,220 --> 00:25:31,820
About your things,

537
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,460
I don't want to stay out of them.

538
00:25:36,260 --> 00:25:37,060
You can come to me

539
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:38,460
whenever

540
00:25:39,650 --> 00:25:40,460
you're in need of help.

541
00:25:43,300 --> 00:25:44,780
Thank you for your kindness.

542
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:02,970
Yunxi?

543
00:26:03,340 --> 00:26:04,180
You're back so early!

544
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:05,580
Where's Qingqing? Did she come back, too?

545
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:06,740
And did she find the three treasures?

546
00:26:07,940 --> 00:26:08,580
Your Highness,

547
00:26:08,820 --> 00:26:10,740
Qingqing hasn't collected all the three treasures.

548
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:11,540
And she hasn't come back.

549
00:26:12,180 --> 00:26:13,140
But don't worry.

550
00:26:13,340 --> 00:26:14,300
She's safe and sound.

551
00:26:16,210 --> 00:26:17,860
On that day, Yunxi told me

552
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:18,660
Qingqing was safe.

553
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:20,700
Then why didn't they meet?

554
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:30,150
[Ciyou Kindergarten]

555
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:45,340
Sister Wan Qing,

556
00:26:45,340 --> 00:26:46,660
what did you call me here for?

557
00:26:50,300 --> 00:26:50,940
Xiaoyi,

558
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:53,780
I'll go out for a couple of days.

559
00:26:54,620 --> 00:26:55,780
I've prepared food for you.

560
00:26:56,130 --> 00:26:56,970
It's in the kitchen.

561
00:26:57,540 --> 00:26:59,180
And I've also washed your clothes.

562
00:26:59,180 --> 00:26:59,900
They're in the wardrobe.

563
00:27:00,700 --> 00:27:01,810
Remember to lock the door

564
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:03,490
when you sleep at night.

565
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:05,300
Besides,

566
00:27:05,540 --> 00:27:06,850
don't go to swim in the river!

567
00:27:07,940 --> 00:27:08,940
Sister Wan Qing.

568
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:10,340
where are you going?

569
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:17,500
I'll go do a thing of my own.

570
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:19,860
And that

571
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:21,740
is my responsibility.

572
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:24,660
I see.

573
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:26,300
Sister Wan Qing,

574
00:27:26,660 --> 00:27:27,340
you once told us

575
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:29,740
that we must be responsible people.

576
00:27:31,980 --> 00:27:33,060
Good boy, Xiaoyi.

577
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:34,860
See you, sister.

578
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:36,690
I'll surely take good care of everyone.

579
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:39,460
Come on, Xiaoyi.

580
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:45,290
Xiaoyi,

581
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:47,220
I'll be back in a couple of days.

582
00:27:49,140 --> 00:27:51,940
But if I don't,

583
00:27:53,490 --> 00:27:54,780
just go to find Brother Sikong.

584
00:27:56,140 --> 00:27:57,300
He will surely take care of you.

585
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:04,900
Father,

586
00:28:05,860 --> 00:28:06,730
I'm back.

587
00:28:07,570 --> 00:28:08,300
Sorry,

588
00:28:08,410 --> 00:28:09,740
I put you through all this trouble.

589
00:28:10,620 --> 00:28:11,900
You're back, Qingqing.

590
00:28:12,260 --> 00:28:12,860
Come here!

591
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:14,500
Let me have a look at you.

592
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:20,900
You've suffered a lot, Qingqing.

593
00:28:21,460 --> 00:28:22,460
I'm fine.

594
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:23,980
But you...

595
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:26,100
I got such a big punishment because of me.

596
00:28:27,020 --> 00:28:27,660
It's okay.

597
00:28:28,860 --> 00:28:32,820
I believe this case will finally be addressed.

598
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:36,020
What did Her Majesty say?

599
00:28:37,140 --> 00:28:39,700
The Crown Prince bought me three days

600
00:28:40,100 --> 00:28:42,300
to find out the truth about the fusang fruit.

601
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:44,060
So long as it comes to light,

602
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:45,380
Lu Mansion will be safe!

603
00:28:46,580 --> 00:28:48,100
Thanks to the Crown Prince.

604
00:28:49,700 --> 00:28:50,220
Qingqing,

605
00:28:51,300 --> 00:28:52,820
you've grown up.

606
00:28:53,500 --> 00:28:56,060
You should be sensible now.

607
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:59,890
The Crown Prince is modest

608
00:29:00,020 --> 00:29:01,260
and generous.

609
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:03,500
He also cares so much about you.

610
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:06,420
You should seize the chance.

611
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:09,220
I also hope you can be happy,

612
00:29:09,580 --> 00:29:11,140
and find the one who really loves you

613
00:29:11,180 --> 00:29:12,100
and cares about you.

614
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:14,780
Only the Crown Prince

615
00:29:14,780 --> 00:29:16,860
can truly protect you.

616
00:29:17,060 --> 00:29:20,020
I know the Crown Prince treat me so well.

617
00:29:21,220 --> 00:29:22,980
But I have no affection

618
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:24,860
for His Highness.

619
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:27,860
Now I only want to find out

620
00:29:27,860 --> 00:29:29,340
the truth about the fusang fruit,

621
00:29:29,860 --> 00:29:31,500
and solve the crisis of Lu Mansion.

622
00:29:32,020 --> 00:29:32,540
Then...

623
00:29:33,290 --> 00:29:34,380
Do you have any ideas about it?

624
00:29:35,810 --> 00:29:39,500
The fusang fruit seems to have been changed by someone.

625
00:29:40,420 --> 00:29:42,180
But I can't figure out who did it.

626
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:47,170
I'm afraid the Crown Prince

627
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:49,540
is the only one who can address it now.

628
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:51,020
The Crown Prince?

629
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:53,220
How?

630
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:56,780
What if you fail to find out the truth in three days?

631
00:29:56,780 --> 00:29:59,660
Only the Crown Prince can save

632
00:29:59,820 --> 00:30:02,100
all the people in our Lu Mansion.

633
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:05,700
I have magic power now.

634
00:30:06,420 --> 00:30:08,810
I can protect not only myself,

635
00:30:09,500 --> 00:30:10,490
but also you,

636
00:30:11,100 --> 00:30:12,420
Baihe, and Yunxi.

637
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:15,180
I'll never let Lu Mansion suffer again!

638
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:17,210
We don't need to bother the Crown Prince.

639
00:30:17,820 --> 00:30:18,540
Really?

640
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:21,300
In Manghuang forest,

641
00:30:21,540 --> 00:30:23,020
I became Master Rongyun's disciple,

642
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:24,020
and practiced my magic power.

643
00:30:24,740 --> 00:30:26,660
Now I've grown much mightier,

644
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:29,100
and have learned a lot.

645
00:30:29,740 --> 00:30:32,420
Who take you to be his disciple?

646
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:33,500
Lord Jin.

647
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:34,700
Lord Jin?

648
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:39,460
Lord Jin is so good to me.

649
00:30:40,300 --> 00:30:42,210
He saved me several times from danger.

650
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:45,100
I know in your eyes,

651
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:46,700
he's no more than a playboy.

652
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:50,740
But I don't think so.

653
00:30:55,450 --> 00:30:56,100
Qingqing,

654
00:30:58,220 --> 00:31:00,860
you and Lord Jin are both unmarried.

655
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:02,060
If you two meet alone

656
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:03,460
frequently,

657
00:31:03,780 --> 00:31:05,220
rumors will spread, I'm afraid.

658
00:31:05,620 --> 00:31:06,170
I don't care.

659
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:12,540
Lord Jin and the Great Commander of No Magic Valley

660
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:13,660
has a close relationship.

661
00:31:14,020 --> 00:31:15,140
If one day,

662
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:17,700
No Magic Valley is in dispute with Qiyuan continent,

663
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:20,860
he can't get away from it.

664
00:31:21,380 --> 00:31:23,460
And if Her Majesty vents her anger on you at that time,

665
00:31:23,660 --> 00:31:25,900
our Lu Family will really be screwed.

666
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:26,580
Father,

667
00:31:27,340 --> 00:31:29,690
No Magic Valley is really now what you think it is.

668
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:37,980
Are you all right, Father?

669
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:40,340
It's okay. It's okay.

670
00:31:41,540 --> 00:31:42,660
I just need to take a rest.

671
00:31:43,420 --> 00:31:44,220
All right, Qingqing.

672
00:31:44,740 --> 00:31:45,450
I'm tired.

673
00:31:46,220 --> 00:31:47,220
You can leave now.

674
00:31:48,460 --> 00:31:49,540
Then please take a good rest.

675
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:37,500
Baihe.

676
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:38,820
Why did you come out?

677
00:32:39,180 --> 00:32:40,090
Your wounds haven't healed yet.

678
00:32:40,220 --> 00:32:41,260
Go back to rest!

679
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,380
I'm fine.

680
00:32:44,380 --> 00:32:46,660
They were all destroyed by the magic power army

681
00:32:46,660 --> 00:32:48,340
after they entered our mansion.

682
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:51,300
You put in a lot of effort for them.

683
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:52,980
What a pity...

684
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:56,860
My lady,

685
00:32:57,530 --> 00:32:58,900
you can cry if you want,

686
00:32:59,540 --> 00:33:00,890
or even curse.

687
00:33:01,060 --> 00:33:01,730
Don't hold yourself back.

688
00:33:02,570 --> 00:33:03,660
I'm heartbroken for you.

689
00:33:08,450 --> 00:33:09,580
Since I got magic power,

690
00:33:10,770 --> 00:33:11,380
I've found

691
00:33:12,180 --> 00:33:14,260
my life kind of hard every day.

692
00:33:14,780 --> 00:33:15,460
My lady,

693
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,180
you've been living a life of confinement for 20 years.

694
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:19,980
And you have magic power now.

695
00:33:20,210 --> 00:33:21,050
Finally, no one can

696
00:33:21,050 --> 00:33:22,900
discriminate against and bully you.

697
00:33:23,500 --> 00:33:26,060
But out of our expectation, there's still so much trouble.

698
00:33:28,060 --> 00:33:29,300
Since it's inevitable,

699
00:33:30,060 --> 00:33:31,020
let me just face it.

700
00:33:32,860 --> 00:33:34,340
Do you think the fusang fruit

701
00:33:34,340 --> 00:33:35,660
was taken away by Commander Qi?

702
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:40,140
I did give the fusang fruit to Qi Yi

703
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:41,820
after I picked it.

704
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:45,740
But you also know what kind of people he is.

705
00:33:46,140 --> 00:33:48,860
And he has no reason to hurt me,

706
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:51,620
or do harm to Lu Mansion.

707
00:33:51,860 --> 00:33:53,820
Then did anyone else

708
00:33:53,820 --> 00:33:54,980
participate in this case?

709
00:33:55,980 --> 00:33:56,980
Anyone else?

710
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:03,610
[Commander's House]

711
00:34:10,010 --> 00:34:11,139
Something's wrong with Sister Wan Qing.

712
00:34:11,380 --> 00:34:11,940
Come!

713
00:34:13,540 --> 00:34:15,139
You all know the thing about the fusang fruit, right?

714
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:18,179
Since Commander Qi came back from Manghuang forest,

715
00:34:18,340 --> 00:34:19,420
was there anything strange in the mansion?

716
00:34:20,090 --> 00:34:21,860
After I gave the fusang fruit to you,

717
00:34:22,820 --> 00:34:24,460
did you pass it on to others?

718
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:26,020
Lady Qingqing,

719
00:34:26,610 --> 00:34:27,699
I swear with my magic power

720
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:28,780
that I really didn't do so.

721
00:34:39,650 --> 00:34:40,219
My lady,

722
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:42,170
I've asked everyone in the mansion.

723
00:34:42,659 --> 00:34:44,380
They all said Commander Qi didn't pass

724
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,219
that package on to others.

725
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:50,130
Then what exactly is the problem?

726
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:05,260
Greetings, Your Highness.

727
00:35:05,740 --> 00:35:06,220
As you were.

728
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:10,660
Your Highness,

729
00:35:11,140 --> 00:35:12,820
what's going on since you come here

730
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:13,980
so early in the morning?

731
00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:16,860
Qingqing was punished because of the fusang fruit,

732
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:18,900
and so was Lu Mansion.

733
00:35:19,700 --> 00:35:20,410
I'm really worried.

734
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:21,980
I think you must

735
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:23,500
feel restless these days, too.

736
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:26,100
It happened all of a sudden.

737
00:35:26,540 --> 00:35:28,940
Father and I are also be troubled by it.

738
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:33,010
I remember

739
00:35:33,820 --> 00:35:35,300
that when you came back from Manghuang forest,

740
00:35:35,740 --> 00:35:36,820
you said Qingqing was fine.

741
00:35:37,580 --> 00:35:38,660
But why did Qingqing say

742
00:35:39,140 --> 00:35:39,900
she didn't meet you?

743
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:42,980
At that time...

744
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:45,060
At that time, I did see Qingqing

745
00:35:45,610 --> 00:35:47,020
I saw she was fine by myself.

746
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:49,340
But Lord Jin was with her.

747
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:50,940
It was improper for me to interrupt.

748
00:35:51,490 --> 00:35:52,940
So I had to come back.

749
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:54,140
Yunxi,

750
00:35:56,130 --> 00:35:57,020
do you know anything

751
00:35:58,700 --> 00:35:59,620
about the fusang fruit?

752
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:02,060
Your Highness, do you suspect me

753
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:04,730
of having something to do with the lost fusang fruit?

754
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:13,180
You've thought too much, Yunxi.

755
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:14,500
It's not like that.

756
00:36:16,260 --> 00:36:17,580
I'm just worried about it.

757
00:36:21,330 --> 00:36:21,820
Your Highness,

758
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:23,580
the fusang fruit was lost.

759
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:26,020
I'm as anxious as Father and Qingqing.

760
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:28,620
I'll surely tell everything I know to them.

761
00:36:29,020 --> 00:36:30,300
Never will I hide anything.

762
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:31,900
Besides,

763
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:33,780
as Qingqing's elder sister,

764
00:36:34,300 --> 00:36:35,700
I won't hide the fusang fruit

765
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:37,460
to entrap my own sister.

766
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:40,820
I was too offensive.

767
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:41,860
Yunxi,

768
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,460
sorry for that.

769
00:36:46,540 --> 00:36:47,780
I feel grateful

770
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:49,660
that you care about our Lu Mansion.

771
00:36:50,460 --> 00:36:51,660
I won't blame you.

772
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,540
If there's any news about the fusang fruit,

773
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:54,780
remember to tell me.

774
00:36:55,540 --> 00:36:56,660
I don't want to see the Lu Family being unjustly accused.

775
00:36:57,540 --> 00:36:58,220
And I also don't want to see

776
00:36:58,940 --> 00:37:00,020
Qingqing being insulted because of it.

777
00:37:05,980 --> 00:37:06,660
I'll go back now.

778
00:37:25,580 --> 00:37:26,140
Wan Qing!

779
00:37:28,540 --> 00:37:28,980
Wan Qing!

780
00:37:31,180 --> 00:37:32,020
Why are you here?

781
00:37:34,140 --> 00:37:35,260
Go out to play for a while.

782
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:38,740
Do you feel all right?

783
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:40,940
Yeah.

784
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:44,940
I knew you two had a quarrel.

785
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:46,060
Brother Sikong,

786
00:37:46,420 --> 00:37:47,460
what did you do

787
00:37:47,460 --> 00:37:49,060
to annoy Sister Wan Qing?

788
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:51,100
Sister Wan Qing

789
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:52,700
seems so unhappy these days.

790
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:55,660
She was even in a trance when knitting just now,

791
00:37:55,820 --> 00:37:56,540
and got her hand pricked.

792
00:37:57,100 --> 00:37:58,100
Wan Qing, you hand...

793
00:37:58,100 --> 00:37:59,060
I-I'm okay.

794
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,930
Xiaoyi was kidding.

795
00:38:01,700 --> 00:38:02,740
I have to cook.

796
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,620
If you're free,

797
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:06,340
stay to have a meal.

798
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:13,860
Brother Sikong,

799
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:16,340
were it not for my letter,

800
00:38:16,540 --> 00:38:17,980
you wouldn't have come back, right?

801
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,380
Xiaoyi, follow me.

802
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:24,500
Xiaoyi,

803
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:25,780
then tell me

804
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:27,610
if your letter is a mischief or not.

805
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:29,340
Did anything happen to Sister Wan Qing?

806
00:38:30,100 --> 00:38:31,380
It's not a mischief!

807
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:34,620
I just found Sister Wan Qing kind of strange.

808
00:38:35,460 --> 00:38:38,020
She held a dagger at night and stared blankly.

809
00:38:54,580 --> 00:38:55,770
Is everything ready?

810
00:38:56,340 --> 00:38:56,860
Yes,

811
00:38:57,020 --> 00:38:57,700
my lord.

812
00:38:58,460 --> 00:38:59,130
Good.

813
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:00,740
Will Lady Qingqing really go to find the Crown Prince?

814
00:39:00,740 --> 00:39:02,220
She hasn't found anything yet,

815
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:03,820
and she's pressed for time.

816
00:39:05,220 --> 00:39:06,260
There's no other choice for her.

817
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:08,300
So long as we act as planned,

818
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:10,500
there's hope for us to get the magic power stone.

819
00:39:12,050 --> 00:39:14,230
[Fengling Hall]

820
00:39:16,500 --> 00:39:17,020
Qi Yi,

821
00:39:17,580 --> 00:39:18,420
I want to ask you something.

822
00:39:18,580 --> 00:39:19,540
Follow me.

823
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:23,700
Lady Yunxi,

824
00:39:24,300 --> 00:39:25,100
what do you want from me?

825
00:39:26,450 --> 00:39:27,060
Qi Yi,

826
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,740
tell me the truth.

827
00:39:29,500 --> 00:39:31,060
Why should Qingqing go to the Crown Prince's palace?

828
00:39:34,180 --> 00:39:34,660
Well...

829
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:37,260
I can't tell you.

830
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:43,380
I didn't expect you've hidden something from me.

831
00:39:43,620 --> 00:39:44,340
Lady Yunxi,

832
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:46,220
I just act as ordered.

833
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:47,540
You've been honest to me

834
00:39:47,860 --> 00:39:48,980
since we were little.

835
00:39:49,300 --> 00:39:50,610
But I didn't expect you wouldn't help me

836
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:52,060
at the critical moment!

837
00:39:52,180 --> 00:39:52,860
Lady Yunxi,

838
00:39:53,770 --> 00:39:55,140
even if I die in front of you today,

839
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:57,130
I still can't say it.

840
00:40:01,220 --> 00:40:01,700
Lady Yunxi,

841
00:40:02,170 --> 00:40:02,900
what are you doing?

842
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:03,940
I won't force you.

843
00:40:04,660 --> 00:40:05,700
I only want to tell you,

844
00:40:06,220 --> 00:40:08,420
today's issue is related to me,

845
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:09,340
and to Lu Mansion.

846
00:40:09,420 --> 00:40:10,380
I can't keep out of it.

847
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:12,140
If I can't solve Father's vexation

848
00:40:12,140 --> 00:40:12,980
